54.000Z","msg":"推 大專戰線加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7733439acac2128e5ee7e54190ec83c96cb1c58","tid":1647354,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"5db4a02c21d5d177a2af0788c1d438e1c512088b","tid":1647354,"uid":99492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7800de2db09ca6cbd8936c19dfb8c7b9760143","tid":1647354,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:27:35.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/